subject: Re: [Read_Alphabet] get your news in QS!
msgSnippet: ... I can create a document with no margins, but then I couldn t print it out myself! How exactly do you print your document? I can make my print larger, too,
messageBody:
Terry Smithwick wrote:
>
>
> The other respondee wanted no or smaller margins so
> he wasn't scrolling around lost on his IPhone. He will
> probably also appreciate two columns.
>
> I want no (or small) margins so I can print the
> text out two to a page and still distinguish the
> letters with these old eyes.

I can create a document with no margins, but then I couldn't print it
out myself! How exactly do you print your document?

I can make my print larger, too, if everyone wanted me to.

Paul

PS Glad to see you got cut and paste to work
